Tiau-khek, chhiuN5-siaN5, chian3-cheng bu2-khi3, cho3 chit8 tiau5 un7-ho5, Bi2-lan5 公爵 hu-jin5 (Beatrics) kap i kiaN2-ji5 e5 siong7, i2-kip8 kiong-lai7 kui3 hu7-jin5 e5 siong7, long2 si7 i chit8 pou7-hun7 e5 chok-phin2.  I siong5-siong5 siuN7 ai3 cho3 ui2-tai7 e5 kang-tiaN5, chiu7-si7 kiong-lai7 sou2 bo5, hi-ki5 e5 mih8.  Ti7 kiong-lai7 u7 siat-ke3 chit8 chiah kim-sai, eng7 au7-kha khia7-teh, chhui3 oe7 thou3-chhut phang-hoe.  Koh u7 cho3 5 sek chin sui2 e5 khong2 chhiok, ia7 u7 cho3 chit8 e5 toa7 liap8 e5 kiu5, choan2-tong7 e5 si5, oe7 chhut im-gak8 e5 siaN.  M7-ku2 Bun5-se Sian-seN bo5 siuN7 an2-ni cho3 kau3-giah8, i sim-lai7 si5-siong5 hi-bong7 cho3-chhut chit8 e5 choe3-toa7 e5 kang-chok, chiu7-si7 ai3 ti7 Seng3 Ma2-li7-a e5 chhiuN5-piah oe7 choe3-au7 Boan2-chhan e5 tou5.
I e5 loe7-sim kio3 i lai5 chhong3-cho7 chit tiuN lang5 sou2 m7-bat piau2-hian7 e5 pi-chham2 chong7-hong2: Chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou choe3-au7 chit8-pai2 chu7-chip8 I 12 e5 su3-tou5, tui3 in kong2, “Lin2 tiong-kan u7 chit8 lang5 beh boe7 goa2.” In chiu7 saN tui3-mng7 ki5-tiong sim2-mih8 lang5 beh choe3 chit e5 tai7-chi3.
Ti7 Bi2-lan5公爵e5 po2-hou7, hou7 Bun5-se Sian-siN khai-si2 i e5 kang-chok, m7-ku2 hut-jian5 Beatrice公爵hu-jin5 kap i e5 gin2-na2 koe3-sin, i chiu7 theng5-khun3 khi3 choe3 in e5 bong7-pai5, in-ui7 i chin keng3-ai3 Beatrice, sou2-i2 ti7 pi-thong3 e5 sim-keng2 cho3 chit e5 chng-thaN7 e5 kang-chok.
Tui3 chit-tiap8 i2-au7, kiong-lai7 toa7 ian3-hoe7 bo5 koh-chai3 khui, an2-ni hoan2-tng2 hou7 i khah u7 si5-kan thang oe7 chit tiuN tou5, m7-ku2 i oe7 tioh8 chin ban7, in-ui7 i hi-bong7 chit tiuN tou5 thang thoan5 chin ku2, cho3 chin-chiaN3 e5 ge7-sut8-phin2, sou2-i2 i tui3 mui2 chit8 tiam2 long2 u7 chhim-chhim e5 kho2-lu7.  ThiaN-kiN3 kong2 i siong5-siong5 khi3 Bi2-lan5 siaN5 e5 ke-lou7 kiaN5-lai5 kiaN5-khi3, tiam7-tiam7 teh bek8-siong2, u7 si5 cheng7-cheng7 che7 teh ki5-to2, siuN7 chin ku2, u7 si5 hui-siong5 jiat8-liat8 kui jit8 ti7 piah-nih8 oe7 tou5, sim7-chi3 boe7 ki3-tit lim chiah8, u7 si5 kong5-kong5 chau2 jip8-lai5, ti7 su3-tou5 e5 bin7 ke chit8-nng7 oeh8 chiu7 koh kong5-kong5 chau2 chhut-khi3.  I put-lun7 sim2-mih8 si5 long2 teh siuN7 kok-e5 su3-tou5 e5 seng3-keh, kap hit si5 e5 piau2-cheng5, i siuN7 kong2 su3-tou5 long2 chham phou2-thong lang5 saN-tang5.  Ti7 i jip8 chiah8-png7-thiaN e5 si5, ia7 si7 long2 teh koan-chhat chiah8-png7 tiong e5 lang5-kheh e5 it-ku2 it-tong7, chaiN2-iuN7 eng7 chhiu2 , kiaN-tioh8 e5 si5, in e5 bak8-bai5 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 tiau3 khi2-lai5. 
Bo5 lang5 chai-iaN2 chit tiuN tou5 si7 oe7 loa7-ku2, u7 lang5 kong2 Ia5-sou e5 thau5 siuN7 chap8 ni5 ku2.  Hit e5 Siu-to7-iN7 e5 thau5-lang5 tong3-boe7-tiau5, sia2 phoe hou7 公爵 kong2, “公爵 hit tiuN piah-tou5 kan-ta chhun Iu5-tai7 e5 thau5-khak iau2-boe7 oan5-seng5; m7-ku2 Bun5-se chit8 ni5 ku2 long2 bo5 lai5 bong chit tiuN choe3-au7 e5 Boan2-chhan lah.” 公爵 chin siu7-khi3, kio3 i lai5, tng-bin7 chiong chit tiuN phoe hou7 i khoaN3.  Bun5-se ia7 toa7 siu7-khi3 kong2, “Chit e5 lang5 tau3-te2 chai-iaN2 sim2-mih8 si7 tou5! I kong2 goa2 chit8 ni5 ku2 bo5 khi3 hia, m7-ku2 an2-ni boe7 thang piau2-si7 goa2 bo5 koan-sim chit tiuN tou5, goa2 tak8-jit8 khi3 ha7-kip sia7-hoe7 chhoe7 goa2 khiam3-eng7 e5 lang5, kau3 taN iau2 chhoe7 long2 bo5 chit8 e5 hah8 goa2 e5 i3-su3, kiam2-chhai2 chit e5 lau7-thau5 kho2-i2 cho3 Iu5-tai7 e5 bou5-heng5.”
