Ng3 Sek-an soaN hng7-hng7 e5 keng2-ti3 e5 thang-a2 hit peng5, Ia5-sou che7 ti7 Iok-han7 kap Se-pi2-thai3 e5 kiaN2 Nga2-kok e5 tiong-kan, I e5 bin7 chhin-chhiuN7 gin2-na2 long2 bo5 sia5-liam7, u7 lin5-bin2 e5 piau2-cheng5.
Chit tiuN tou5 tau3-ti2 oan5-seng5 liau2 a2-boe7? Kin-ku3 lek8-su2 e5 ki3-chai3, ti7 1499 ni5, Hoat-kok Louis u7 chin3-kun jip8 I3-tai7-li7, tui3 Bi2-lan5 koaN2-chhut 公爵, hit si5 Bun5-se Sian-siN iau2-ku2 teh siu-cheng2 chit tiuN beng5-oe7, bo5 loa7-ku2 i ia7 hou7 lang5 koaN2-chhut Bi2-lan5, sou2-i2 chit tiuN tou5 ti7 Bun5-se Sian-siN e5 sim-tiong si7 iau2-boe7 oan5-seng5, Louis kau3 Bi2-lan5 chiu7 sui5-si5 chau2-khi3 Seng3 Ma2-li7-a Siu-to7-iN7 khoaN3 chit tiuN Seng3-oe7 “Choe3-au7 e5 Boan2-chhan,” khoaN3 chin ku2, m7-kam li7-khui; chiu7 kio3 i e5 pou7-ha7 ka7 in kong2, “Chiong chit e5 kut8 tng2-lai5 Hoat-kok.” Ti7 chit e5 pho3-hoai7 kang-chok i2-cheng5, u7 chhut chit8 e5 sin5-jiah, chiu7-si7 u7 lang5 tui3 i tiong-ko3, i chiu7 po2-choan5 chit e5 bo5 hou7 lang5 pho3-hoai7, m7-ku2 ki5-thaN Bi2-lan5 siaN5-lai7 e5 ho2 mih8 long2 chhiuN2 kau3 khang-khang.  
